import {gql} from '@apollo/client'

export const ORDERS=gql`
query Query($ouser_id: ID!) {
    orders(ouser_id: $ouser_id) {
      ouser_id
      oproduct_id {
        _id
        productname
        price
        shopname
        image
        category
        description
        count
        
        sales
      }
      oquantity
      odate
      checked
    }
    
  }`

  export const LOGIN=gql`
  query Login($emailid: String!, $password: String!) {
    login(emailid: $emailid, password: $password) {
      _id
      emailid
      name
      shopname
      shopImage
      profileimage
      gender
      country
      dob
      about
      address
      phone
    }
  }`
